      • augmentToStringFields

        protected void augmentToStringFields(Map<String,Object> augmentedToStringFields)
        optionally adds extra "fields" that should be included in #toString. This implementation adds no extra fields but is meant for subclasses to use.
        Parameters:
        augmentedToStringFields - a map of the names of field names to their values as Objects to be augmented by extra "fields" that should be included in #toString
        See Also:
        toString()

      • toString

        public String toString()
        uses reflection to include all fields, in addition to added fields from #augmentToStringFields
